{"tid":662734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當錢唔再係問題既時候，你係咪就會開心？","createTime":"2018-05-12T16:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T05:33:14.000Z","uid":171277,"like":22,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca3d5565fbe9d5bf1de1da53f4ba22a60ab2bd0","tid":662734,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"屋企4個人，1個家姐，屋企唔係中產，但都算衣食無憂，係小康之家<br />\n<br />\n19ft+ 19pt 一個星期番足7日，一個月total有2萬幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n扣晒學費家用同其他支出，每個月其實有皮幾野淨<br />\n<br />\n雖然買唔起樓，但錢對我目前生活黎講完全唔係問題，買想要既野其實可以唔洗睇價錢（幾百至幾千），不過冇咩意慾買<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解冇乜開心既感覺，做咩都好無熱誠<br />\n<br />\n有人話我番得太多工唔放假所以咁頹，開頭我係覺得自己人工低先番多份pt，但我開始發覺比起錢，我應該係精神上唔滿足，所以先搞到自己咁忙<br />\n<br />\n但究竟做咩先滿足到我，我唔知<br />\n<br />\ne加久唔久就會m到咁，覺得個人好迷失唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076731dfee2a868835abfec70df92f5b51676959","tid":662734,"uid":5591,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"皮幾兩皮野上連登講錢唔再係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d819ce3757534e80da21f2d76413e7b2cb2574","tid":662734,"uid":171277,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"076731dfee2a868835abfec70df92f5b51676959","tid":662734,"uid":5591,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"皮幾兩皮野上連登講錢唔再係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"睇你target買乜"},{"pid":"2ec51cb6cb130872a3f543e9450295cbbb75c4ba","tid":662734,"uid":81213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"試吓增高"},{"pid":"0dc67fab4ae9783530f2752d0e8d72109593b5b7","tid":662734,"uid":37728,"like":