class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇你e刻目標係用錢買咩ja，我買d平民野2皮野真係唔會用得晒<br />\n<br />\n就算一星期有兩萬，轉頭都又有人話一星期有4萬先出聲，永遠有野買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人對物質欲望係無止境<br />\n 就算你去到誠哥咁既級數 都會煩緊點搵錢再買左另一樣野，做到90歲先退休"},{"pid":"1a313e8524912c9a4190c871dc912941e92a39e8","tid":662734,"uid":112161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ca3d5565fbe9d5bf1de1da53f4ba22a60ab2bd0","tid":662734,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"屋企4個人，1個家姐，屋企唔係中產，但都算衣食無憂，係小康之家<br />\n<br />\n19ft+ 19pt 一個星期番足7日，一個月total有2萬幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n扣晒學費家用同其他支出，每個月其實有皮幾野淨<br />\n<br />\n雖然買唔起樓，但錢對我目前生活黎講完全唔係問題，買想要既野其實可以唔洗睇價錢（幾百至幾千），不過冇咩意慾買<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解冇乜開心既感覺，做咩都好無熱誠<br />\n<br />\n有人話我番得太多工唔放假所以咁頹，開頭我係覺得自己人工低先番多份pt，但我開始發覺比起錢，我應該係精神上唔滿足，所以先搞到自己咁忙<br />\n<br />\n但究竟做咩先滿足到我，我唔知<br />\n<br />\ne加久唔久就會m到咁，覺得個人好迷失唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"人生，要冒險還是無風險？(長文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/662612/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/662612/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34dc20906777977b92f22347f9b562a570cc7b41","tid":662734,"uid":104699,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/112156_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F112156_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=aab51026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d24c223a1f153675e8bc457a5e348515bd4f826","tid":662734,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"萬幾銀對大部份夠錢駛既家庭黎講食野都駛左 點解你會話唔係問題 平時食開大快活？"},{"pid":"8474c6d4def5b87a799e46090c540e49694454d1","tid":662734,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d24c223a1f153675e8bc457a5e348515bd4f826","tid":662734,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"萬幾銀對大部份夠錢駛既家庭黎講食野都駛左 點解你會話唔係問題 平時食開大快活？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   咁上下消費"},{"pid":"fbe79ca1d8b33d8275de5497c38887bd1658b8f8","tid":662734,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗翻牛工又有錢先最撚開心<br />\n<br />\n你呢家只係用時間換錢又點會開心"},{"pid":"d0ab9c26e0bd0ea8ab82db2f6ab9dcd102365971","tid":662734,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"搵返個伴侶囉<br />\n到時你一係好開心 一係煩到仆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05bf3c18efb9f7c1bf13e041fc169a45bbaf5a2","tid":662734,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"未入po 我以為樓主係有幾多億身家 已經玩到無野想玩咁高層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望到2皮幾一個月再加原來無樓 係香港講錢唔係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話錢唔係問題 同無快樂 只係因為你太少錢 可以享受到嘅野太少同你未發生要用錢解決嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n到你有一日 可以選擇做定唔做 你仲可以繼續維持住一貫生活 唔使再去搵錢先再開呢個po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beb34435ebadf91772d2fb4623c11c66b8dd224","tid":662734,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"唔會，同樓主差唔多，對讀緊書既我黎講一個月大約$10-20K收入算好滿足，又唔駛比家用，父母仲另外比零用我，仲預左筆錢比我買樓，但一D都唔覺得開心，就算有兄弟有另一半，最多都係同佢地一齊時開心，但都分唔到係真開心定扮出黎，有時夜晚個個訓哂教自己戇鳩鳩係廳直頭會諗生存為乜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7e5963033ab7646e1b2d0df71c6a57b0a1b3ed","tid":662734,"uid":135340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b866163240f0042fb359ac8456d55b1664fc8f9","tid":662734,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4055c61f0cba8481ea62034211621558e9b4d7e0","tid":662734,"uid":135340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:36:28.000Z","msg":"因為除左為腦細工作之外你乜追求慾望都無<br />\n一個無自己理想抱負 甚至連興趣都無<br />\n全部時間貢獻曬比工作嘅人點會開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"對工作有熱誠去投入係一件好事<br />\n但係當你盲目地去投入就係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得有人講過 當你生活去到一個點 就係你過於安於現狀 已經無動力去作出改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一件好恐怖既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d7fe1e581ab92214317485a78fff6703a99989","tid":662734,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/131452_9c3430dba6c387b09f0c14672c90118d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F131452_9c3430dba6c387b09f0c14672c90118d.png&h=f18a746a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77350393fa531ddee528a671a8bf56642afb29cd","tid":662734,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"有錢你都無時間洗，點開心啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}